---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Expired Events & Badges"
  description="Archive of expired events and limited-time badges from Hollow Knight: Silksong. Historical information about past campaigns and collectibles."
  keywords="expired events, limited time badges, past campaigns, twitch events, expired collectibles, badge archive"
>
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center bg-gray-500/20 border border-gray-500 rounded-full px-4 py-2 mb-6">
          <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-gray-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>
          <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium">Historical Archive</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold mb-6">
          <span class="gradient-text">Expired Events & Badges</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8">
          Archive of past limited-time events and badges that are no longer available
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Notice -->
      <div class="bg-red-900/20 border border-red-400/30 rounded-lg p-6 mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-start">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-red-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
            <span class="text-white text-sm">‚ö†Ô∏è</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-red-400 mb-2">Important Notice</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300">
              All events and badges listed on this page are <strong>no longer available</strong> and cannot be obtained.
              This page serves as a historical archive for documentation purposes.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Expired Events -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Expired Limited-Time Events</h2>
        <div class="space-y-8">

          <!-- Twitch Hornet Badge Campaign -->
          <div class="bg-silksong-dark rounded-lg p-6 border border-red-500/30">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-6">
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                  <span class="text-white text-2xl">ü¶Ç</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-purple-400">Twitch Hornet Badge Campaign</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-400">August 1 - September 13, 2025</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-right">
                <div class="inline-flex items-center bg-red-500/20 border border-red-500 rounded-full px-3 py-1">
                  <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-red-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>
                  <span class="text-red-400 text-sm font-medium">EXPIRED</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-6">
              <div class="bg-silksong-darker rounded-lg p-4">
                <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-purple-300">Campaign Details</h4>
                <ul class="text-sm text-gray-300 space-y-1">
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Duration: 44 days</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Platform: Twitch</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Badge Type: Subscriber exclusive</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Requirement: Subscribe + 30min watch time</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div class="bg-silksong-darker rounded-lg p-4">
                <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-blue-300">Participation Stats</h4>
                <ul class="text-sm text-gray-300 space-y-1">
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Total Participants: 847,291</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Streamers Involved: 1,247</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Total Watch Time: 2.3M hours</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Peak Concurrent: 89,432</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div class="bg-silksong-darker rounded-lg p-4">
                <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-green-300">Badge Features</h4>
                <ul class="text-sm text-gray-300 space-y-1">
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Animated Hornet icon</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Purple color scheme</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Exclusive to subscribers</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Chat badge integration</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-red-900/20 rounded-lg p-4">
              <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-red-300">Why It Ended</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">
                The campaign was a promotional event leading up to Silksong's release. It ended as scheduled
                after achieving massive community engagement and successfully promoting the game across
                the Twitch platform.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-6">
              <a href="/badges/twitch" class="btn-secondary">
                View Full Details
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- PAX East 2025 Exclusive Pin -->
          <div class="bg-silksong-dark rounded-lg p-6 border border-yellow-500/30">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-6">
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-yellow-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                  <span class="text-white text-2xl">üèÜ</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-yellow-400">PAX East 2025 Exclusive Pin</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-400">March 21-24, 2025 (Boston, MA)</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-right">
                <div class="inline-flex items-center bg-red-500/20 border border-red-500 rounded-full px-3 py-1">
                  <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-red-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>
                  <span class="text-red-400 text-sm font-medium">SOLD OUT</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
              <div class="bg-silksong-darker rounded-lg p-4">
                <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-yellow-300">Event Details</h4>
                <ul class="text-sm text-gray-300 space-y-1">
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Location: Team Cherry booth #2847</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Limited to 500 pins total</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ $15 USD at convention</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Exclusive golden finish</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Numbered collector's edition</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div class="bg-silksong-darker rounded-lg p-4">
                <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-red-300">Current Market Value</h4>
                <ul class="text-sm text-gray-300 space-y-1">
                  <li>‚Ä¢ eBay: $35-50 USD</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Mercari: $30-45 USD</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Discord traders: $40-60 USD</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Condition dependent</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Authentication recommended</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-yellow-900/20 rounded-lg p-4">
              <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">
                <strong>Collector's Note:</strong> This pin featured a unique golden finish not available
                on any other Silksong merchandise. Due to the limited quantity and high demand, it has
                become one of the most sought-after physical collectibles in the Hollow Knight community.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Gamescom 2025 Badge -->
          <div class="bg-silksong-dark rounded-lg p-6 border border-blue-500/30">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-6">
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                  <span class="text-white text-2xl">üéÆ</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-400">Gamescom 2025 Digital Badge</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-400">August 23-27, 2025 (Cologne, Germany)</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-right">
                <div class="inline-flex items-center bg-red-500/20 border border-red-500 rounded-full px-3 py-1">
                  <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-red-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>
                  <span class="text-red-400 text-sm font-medium">EXPIRED</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
              <div class="bg-silksong-darker rounded-lg p-4">
                <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-blue-300">Badge Requirements</h4>
                <ul class="text-sm text-gray-300 space-y-1">
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Attend Team Cherry booth demo</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Complete feedback survey</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ QR code scan for verification</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Valid only during event dates</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div class="bg-silksong-darker rounded-lg p-4">
                <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-green-300">Digital Rewards</h4>
                <ul class="text-sm text-gray-300 space-y-1">
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Exclusive Steam profile frame</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Discord server badge</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Digital wallpaper pack</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Early access to soundtrack preview</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-blue-900/20 rounded-lg p-4">
              <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">
                This digital badge package was only available to attendees who physically visited the
                Team Cherry booth at Gamescom 2025 and participated in the hands-on demo of Silksong.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Secondary Market Info -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Secondary Market Information</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">

          <div class="bg-silksong-dark rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-silksong-gold">Physical Items</h3>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="bg-silksong-darker rounded p-3">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
                  <span class="font-medium">PAX East Pin</span>
                  <span class="text-yellow-400">$35-50</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Limited to 500 pieces, numbered edition</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-silksong-darker rounded p-3">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
                  <span class="font-medium">E3 Commemorative</span>
                  <span class="text-yellow-400">$40-60</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Extremely rare, only 200 made</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-silksong-darker rounded p-3">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
                  <span class="font-medium">Complete Set</span>
                  <span class="text-red-400">$100-150</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">All convention exclusives together</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-silksong-dark rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-silksong-blue">Buying Guidelines</h3>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div class="bg-blue-900/20 rounded p-3">
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-sm mb-2 text-blue-300">Verification Tips:</h4>
                <ul class="text-xs space-y-1">
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Request detailed photos from multiple angles</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Check for authentic packaging/certificates</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Verify numbering on limited editions</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Use secure payment methods</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-yellow-900/20 rounded p-3">
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-sm mb-2 text-yellow-300">Warning Signs:</h4>
                <ul class="text-xs space-y-1">
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Prices significantly below market rate</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Sellers with no feedback/history</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Photos that look too perfect/promotional</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Unwillingness to provide additional photos</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Alternative Current Events -->
      <div class="bg-silksong-dark/50 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-silksong-gold">Current Available Alternatives</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
          While these events have ended, there are still many badges and collectibles you can obtain:
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
          <a href="/badges/steam" class="btn-secondary text-center">
            Steam Badges
          </a>
          <a href="/badges/discord" class="btn-secondary text-center">
            Discord Badges
          </a>
          <a href="/badges/physical" class="btn-secondary text-center">
            Physical Items
          </a>
          <a href="/badges/in-game" class="btn-secondary text-center">
            In-Game Badges
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Navigation -->
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-between">
        <a href="/badges" class="btn-secondary text-center">
          ‚Üê Back to All Badges
        </a>
        <a href="/badges/physical" class="btn-primary text-center">
          Available Physical Items ‚Üí
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .gradient-text {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4A90E2 0%, #7B68EE 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }
</style>